\c 16
\s Jehovha acharova VaJudha
\p
\v 1 Zvino shoko raJehovha rakasvika kwandiri richiti:
\v 2 Usazvitorera mukadzi, uye usava nevanakomana kana vakunda panzvimbo ino.
\v 3 Nokuti anoreva seizvi Jehovha pamusoro pevanakomana nepamusoro pevanasikana vanoberekerwa panzvimbo ino, nepamusoro pana amai vavo vakavabereka, nepamusoro pemadzibaba avo akavabereka panyika ino:
\v 4 Vachafa nerufu rwunorwadza; havangachemwi, uye havangavigwi, vachava semupfudze pamusoro pechiso chenyika; uye vachapedzwa nemunondo uye nenzara; nezvitunha zvavo zvichava zvekudya zveshiri dzekumatenga nezvemhuka dzenyika.
\v 5 Nokuti anoreva seizvi Jehovha: Usapinda muimba yekuchema, uye usaenda kunoungudza kana kuvachema; nokuti ndabvisa rugare rwangu pavanhu ava, anoreva Jehovha, rudo rweunyoro hwangu nenyasha dzangu.
\p
\v 6 Zvino vakuru nevadiki vachafa panyika ino, havangavigwi, uye havangavachemi, kana kuzvigura kana kuzvivevura nekuda kwavo.
\v 7 Uye havangavaguriri \add chingwa \add* pakuchema kwavo, kuvanyaradza pamusoro pevakafa, uye havangavapi mukombe wenyaradzo kuti vanwe nekuda kwebaba vavo kana mai vavo.
\v 8 Newe usapinda muimba yemabiko, kuti ugare navo kuti udye nekunwa.
\v 9 Nokuti anoreva seizvi Jehovha wehondo Mwari waIsraeri: Tarirai, ndichagumisa panzvimbo ino, pameso penyu uye pamazuva enyu, inzwi remufaro neinzwi rekupembera, neinzwi rechikomba, neinzwi remwenga.
\p
\v 10 Zvino zvichaitika pauchaudza vanhu ava mashoko awa ese, zvino vachati kwauri: Sei Jehovha ataura mashoko awa ese kuvanhu ava? Uye vachati kwauri: Jehovha wataurirei chakaipa chese chikuru ichi kwatiri? Kana: Kuipa kwedu ndekupi? Kana Chivi chedu chatakaitira Jehovha Mwari ndechipi?
\v 11 Ipapo uchati kwavari: Nokuti madzibaba enyu akandisiya, anoreva Jehovha, uye vakafamba vachitevera vamwe vamwari, uye vakavashumira, uye vakavakotamira, ndokusiya ini, uye havana kuchengeta murairo wangu;
\v 12 zvino imwi makaita zvakaipa kupfuura madzibaba enyu; nokuti tarirai, munofamba umwe neumwe acitevera ukukutu hwemoyo wake wakaipa, kuti vasanditeerera.
\v 13 Naizvozvo ndichakurasirai kunze kwenyika ino kuenda kunyika yamusingazivi, imwi nemadzibaba enyu, uye ikoko muchanoshumira vamwe vamwari masikati neusiku, kwandisingakunzwiriyi nyasha.
\p
\v 14 Naizvozvo tarirai, mazuva anouya, anoreva Jehovha, kuti hakuchazonzi: NaJehovha mupenyu, wakakwidza vana vaIsraeri kubva munyika yeEgipita;
\v 15 asi NaJehovha mupenyu, wakakwidza vana vaIsraeri kubva kunyika yekumaodzanyemba, uye kunyika dzese dzaaiva avadzingira kwadziri; nokuti ndichavadzosazve kunyika yekwavo yandakapa madzibaba avo.
\p
\v 16 Tarirai, ndichatumira kunodana varedzi vazhinji vehove, anoreva Jehovha; zvino vachavaredza, uye shure kweizvozvo ndichatumira \add kunodana\add* vavhimi vazhinji, zvino vachavavhima pamakomo ese nepachikomo chipi nechipi, uye kubva mumapako emabwe.
\v 17 Nokuti meso angu ari pamusoro penzira dzavo dzese, hadzina kuvanzwa pachiso changu, nekuipa kwavo hakuna kuvanzwa pameso angu.
\v 18 Zvino kutanga ndichatsiva kuipa kwavo nechivi chavo kakapetwa kaviri, nokuti vakasvibisa nyika yangu, vakazadza nhaka yangu nezvitunha zvezvinosemesa nezvinyangadzo zvavo.
\p
\v 19 Imwi Jehovha, simba rangu, nenhare yangu, neutiziro hwangu pazuva rekutambudzika, marudzi achauya kwamuri kubva kumigumo yenyika, achiti: Zvirokwazvo madzibaba edu akagara nhaka yenhema, zvisina maturo, musina batsiro mazviri.
\v 20 Munhu ungazviitira vamwari vasati vari vamwari here?
\v 21 Naizvozvo, tarirai, ndichavazivisa ruoko rwangu nesimba rangu; zvino vachaziva kuti zita rangu ndiJehovha.